<h2>Customized Application Store</h2>

<p>
Werner would like to provide his application to a broad audience while
ensuring that it is uniquely customized to each of his customers. He has
experience writing code and would like every application package that
is distributed to have a unique customer key embedded in the installation
program.
</p>

